{"parentUuid":"aca244a6-a256-4a75-9b13-7b65548f74be","isSidechain":false,"message":{"id":"8e63cc24-de4c-4b05-8a5e-21e2d3a0f9f2","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"deepseek-v4-pro","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture. Let me categorize what's missing from the game maps:\n\n**Major locations in the novel that are MISSING from game maps:**\n\n1. **天涯城** (x41) - Critical! This is the transit city between 黑角域 and 中州. The novel describes it as the ONLY city within a thousand miles that has space wormholes to 中州.\n\n2. **化骨城** (x15) - A transit city near 黑角域\n\n3. **天罡殿** (x11) - 魂殿's main headquarters (contains 人殿, 地殿, 天殿)\n\n4. **人殿** (x44), **地殿** (x2), **天殿** (x2) - Sub-locations of 天罡殿/魂殿\n\n5. **萧家** (x1025) - Very frequently mentioned. While we have `map_xiao_mansion` (萧家府邸), 萧家 as a broader concept appears extensively.\n\n6. **萧门** (x330) - 萧炎在迦南学院内院建立的势力 (already in engine.py as 磐门)\n\n7. **天冥宗** (x233), **玄冥宗** (x89), **冥河盟** (x95) - 中州宗门\n\n8. **中域** (x69), **中州南域** (x4), **中州西域** (x10), **中州东域** (x4) - Sub-regions of 中州\n\n9. **天山血潭** (x167) - Important training location in 中州\n\n10. **天目山脉** (x123) - Where 天山血潭 is located\n\n11. **风雷北阁** (x155), **风雷东阁** (x5), **风雷西阁** (x1) - Sub-branches of 风雷阁\n\n12. **丹界** (x137) - 药族/丹塔相关空间\n\n13. **空间交易会** (x50) - Important trading event/location\n\n14. **异火广场** (x25) - Where 陀舍古帝's inheritance is\n\n15. **加玛圣城** (x33) - Another name for 加玛帝都\n\n16. **镇鬼关** (x34) - Border pass\n\n17. **大岭城** (x13) - Border city\n\n18. **落雁帝国** (x6), **慕兰帝国** (x2) - Neighboring empires\n\n19. **灵界** (x10), **雷界** (x1) - 远古种族空间\n\n20. **妖火平原** (x7) - Related to 净莲妖火\n\n21. **星陨峰** (x4) - Related to 星陨阁\n\n22. **黑盟** (x125) - 黑角域联盟\n\n23. **血宗** (x102) - 黑角域势力\n\n24. **八扇门** (x19) - 黑印城势力\n\nNow, let me also look specifically for the travel route descriptions. The novel's key travel routes are:\n\n1. **加玛帝国 → 黑角域**: No space wormhole. Very long overland journey. Passes through many small countries.\n\n2. **黑角域 → 中州**: Through 天涯城 (has space wormhole to 中州). Only 斗尊 level experts can maintain wormholes.\n\n3. **中州 internal**: Space wormholes between major cities/regions.\n\n4. **中州 → 龙岛**: Through 虚空 (void) using 空间船 or 斗圣-level ability.\n\n5. **中州 → 远古种族空间 (古界, 魂界, etc.)**: Using specific 空间通道 or portals.\n\nNow let me also find what specific locations from the novel are already covered by game maps and what the key gaps are.\n\nLet me now create a comprehensive comparison table. Let me also search for specific sections about the 天涯城 transit hub.","signature":"8e63cc24-de4c-4b05-8a5e-21e2d3a0f9f2"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":822,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":107136,"output_tokens":1169,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"stop_details":null},"type":"assistant","uuid":"5acc5a96-9688-4e24-97e7-4c7f92f3f968","timestamp":"2026-06-09T00:57:53.885Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"D:\\work\\wordworld","sessionId":"00d28fbf-7def-43f1-8f03-9196876513ea","version":"2.1.169","gitBranch":"master","slug":"eager-weaving-neumann"}
