ngine.\n\nActually, re-reading the user's request: \"各区域之前的如何通行方式要跟原文一致\" - this is about how regions connect. The most important aspect is:\n1. 天涯城 is the transit hub between 黑角域 and 中州 (not direct)\n2. No 传送阵 (which the game already doesn't have)\n3. 沙漠区域需要经过特定边塞城市\n\nFor now, I think the most impactful thing is to make sure the descriptions and unlock logic are correct. The new maps are unlocked at appropriate story phases, so the player naturally encounters them in sequence.\n\nLet me also make sure I haven't introduced errors. Let me verify the engine loads correctly.\n\nAlso, I should create a travel_route configuration. Let me think... That's a big change. Let me focus on what's most practical and impactful now.\n\nActually let me at least add the concept of travel restrictions. In the novel:\n- To go from 加玛帝国 to 黑角域, you need to pass through the border garrisons and 黑域大平原\n- To go from 黑角域 to 中州, you MUST go through 天涯城 (the only wormhole)\n- To go from 中州 to 龙岛, you need a 空间船 or 斗圣 level\n\nI could implement a simple travel restriction by adding a `travel_restriction` to maps that checks prerequisites. But this is complex...\n\nLet me verify the engine loads correctly first.","signature":"4bb34420-112b-4025-8eab-de800a2aebd5"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":981,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":139904,"output_tokens":1545,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"stop_details":null},"type":"assistant","uuid":"ccff2afd-796a-4556-a29f-a728e7c37625","timestamp":"2026-06-09T01:10:50.542Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"D:\\work\\wordworld","sessionId":"00d28fbf-7def-43f1-8f03-9196876513ea","version":"2.1.169","gitBranch":"master","slug":"eager-weaving-neumann"}
