ed:**\n\nMAPS:\n1. 大岭城 - border city between 加玛 and 黑角域\n2. 黑域大平原 - transit area\n3. 化骨城 - 黑角域 border city\n\nNPCS:\nFrom the scan, the genuinely missing NPCs are:\n- 柳翎 (252次) - 法犸弟子，炼药天才\n- 谷尼 (90次) - 二品炼药师，与雅妃在乌坦城工作\n- 木战 (129次) - 木家，迦南学院\n- 妖暝 (46次) - 九幽地冥蟒族前族长\n- 九天尊 (225次) - 魂殿九天尊（多位尊者）\n\nPLACES TO ADD（章节发现的新地点）:\n- 炙火山脉 (near 焚炎谷)\n- 栖凤山 (风雷阁相关)\n- 天黄城 (中域城市)\n- 黑皇阁 (黑皇宗的接待场所)\n- 黑火宗 (中州宗门)\n- 万药山脉 (丹界入口附近)\n- 莽荒镇 (莽荒古域外的镇子)\n- 天魔血池 (莽荒古域内)\n- 古域台 (莽荒古域内)\n- 古殿 (莽荒古域/远古遗迹)\n- 小丹塔 (丹塔内部圣地)\n- 葬天山脉 (最终战地点之一)\n\nLet me now create a comprehensive script to add all these. I'll need to:\n1. Add missing NPCs\n2. Add missing maps\n3. Add encounters for new maps\n4. Update engine.py\n\nThis is a lot of content. Let me focus on the most important ones first - the ones with high occurrence counts that are clearly important.\n\nActually, let me be smarter about this. Let me first check which NPCs are genuinely missing (not just using short names in the scan).","signature":"6739c827-5d0e-4c34-ba5e-6b0537e03d4b"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":120,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":224896,"output_tokens":1618,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"stop_details":null},"type":"assistant","uuid":"3ed6eff6-c92f-4750-884f-57beed72067b","timestamp":"2026-06-09T02:03:25.401Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"D:\\work\\wordworld","sessionId":"00d28fbf-7def-43f1-8f03-9196876513ea","version":"2.1.169","gitBranch":"master","slug":"eager-weaving-neumann"}
