{"parentUuid":"be8355d5-3138-405e-b0ad-4b41600ec44b","isSidechain":false,"message":{"id":"10fb756c-bff5-48f4-b2e0-f6029f887702","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"deepseek-v4-pro","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants:\n1. At least 100 common mobs\n2. At least 100 elite enemies\n3. Bosses following the original novel\n4. Some \"boss\" characters should NOT be killable because they can later develop relationships (e.g., 美杜莎/彩鳞, 云韵, 小医仙, etc.)\n\nThis is a massive task. Let me plan it carefully:\n\n**Characters that are \"bosses\" in combat but shouldn't be permanently killed:**\n- 美杜莎/彩鳞 - later becomes ally/wife\n- 云韵 - later becomes ally\n- 小医仙 - initially hostile as 毒宗宗主, later ally\n- 海波东 - initially fought, later ally\n- 韩枫 - killed in novel (soul escapes to 魂殿)\n- 纳兰嫣然 - defeated but not killed\n\nFor these characters, I need to add a \"can_spare\" or \"non_lethal\" flag, and have the combat result be \"defeated\" rather than \"killed\", allowing relationship development afterward.\n\nActually, looking at the current code, the engine handles combat with `win_next` and `lose_next` fields. The \"killing\" is implicit. What I need is:\n- For non-lethal bosses: winning the fight doesn't remove the NPC, it just changes the relationship\n- For lethal bosses: winning the fight removes the NPC permanently\n\nBut this is a deep engine change. Let me focus on what the user asked:\n1. Add 100+ common mobs\n2. Add 100+ elites\n3. Add bosses per the novel\n4. Mark which bosses are \"non-lethal\" (can develop relationships later)\n\nLet me organize the enemies by the novel's regions and timeline.\n\n**Common Mobs (by region):**\n- 魔兽山脉: 1-3阶魔兽各系 (wind wolf, fire serpent, ice bear, earth boar, etc.) - ~20\n- 塔戈尔沙漠: 沙蝎, 沙蛇, 沙漠盗匪, 蛇人族巡逻兵 - ~15\n- 黑角域: 流寇, 亡命徒, 血宗弟子, 黑盟杂兵 - ~15\n- 迦南学院: 陪练弟子, 考核傀儡 - ~5\n- 中州: 散修, 四方阁外围弟子, 各宗杂役 - ~20\n- 魂殿: 魂使, 锁魂使, 魂殿杂兵 - ~10\n- 兽域: 各系高阶魔兽 - ~10\n- 龙岛: 龙族卫士 - ~5\n- 莽荒古域: 远古兽 - ~5\n- 其他: ~5\nTotal: ~110\n\n**Elite Enemies (by region):**\n- 加玛帝国: 各城强者, 佣兵团长, 宗门执事 - ~15\n- 出云帝国: 毒宗长老, 万蝎门长老, 金雁宗/慕兰谷强者 - ~10\n- 黑角域: 血宗长老, 黑盟头目, 各势力中层 - ~15\n- 迦南学院: 强榜高手, 执法队 - ~10\n- 中州: 四方阁长老, 各宗门精英, 丹塔执事 - ~20\n- 魂殿: 魂殿护法, 天尊 - ~15\n- 兽域: 化形魔兽 - ~10\n- 龙岛: 龙族将领 - ~5\n- 远古种族: 各族精英 - ~10\nTotal: ~110\n\n**Bosses (per novel):**\nAlready have many, need to add more per the novel and mark non-lethal ones.\n\nLet me write a big comprehensive script. This is going to be very long.\n\nActually, given the massive scope, let me write this as a comprehensive script that generates all enemy data. I'll organize by region and type.\n\nFor the \"non-lethal boss\" concept, I'll add a simple \"can_kill\" field (or use the Notes field to mark it). The engine already has a combat system - for non-lethal bosses, the win_next can point to a \"spared\" event instead of a death event.\n\nLet me start writing the script.","signature":"10fb756c-bff5-48f4-b2e0-f6029f887702"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":161,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":271616,"output_tokens":1077,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"stop_details":null},"type":"assistant","uuid":"75d63ca1-af16-414c-9752-878e0e8f5ebc","timestamp":"2026-06-09T02:42:51.010Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"D:\\work\\wordworld","sessionId":"00d28fbf-7def-43f1-8f03-9196876513ea","version":"2.1.169","gitBranch":"master","slug":"eager-weaving-neumann"}
