{"parentUuid":"33f69789-8a02-4b28-8952-ec94dd97de91","isSidechain":false,"message":{"id":"0c465330-7e30-4040-be73-1923b49c2a48","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"deepseek-v4-pro","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The scan reveals several problems:\n\n1. **Many elites have generic skills** - most elites just got 剑气+斗气护体+掌法, which is wrong for named characters\n2. **Many bosses have generic skills** - bosses like 地魔老鬼, 莫天行, 金银二老 got generic skills instead of their actual novel abilities\n3. **Some skill IDs show as \"?\"** - these are skills referenced in the ENEMY_NOVEL_SKILLS dict that don't exist in the skills table yet\n4. **21 elites have ≤2 skills** - too few\n\nThe core issue: I only mapped ~45 characters in ENEMY_NOVEL_SKILLS, but there are 146+70=216 elite+boss enemies. Most of them fell through to the generic mob skill function.\n\nLet me fix this properly:\n1. Search the novel for every named elite/boss that doesn't have proper skills\n2. Assign their canonical abilities\n3. Create any missing skills\n\nLet me identify which enemies specifically need attention:\n\nBosses with generic skills (only 3 generic skills instead of unique ones):\n- 穆蛇, 双头火灵蛇, 紫晶翼狮王, 沙盗之王, 沙漠古蝎王, 神殿守护兽, 火猿王\n- 八扇门主, 黑印城地下之主, 黑角域竞技场之王\n- 内院守护者, 天焚炼气塔兽王\n- 金雁宗宗主, 慕兰谷谷主\n- 黑火老祖, 丹塔守护者, 空间交易会会长, 万药山脉之主, 莽荒镇长, 小丹塔大长老, 葬天山脉守护者\n- 冥蟒篡位者, 天妖凰族长老\n- 古龙王残魂\n- 古族大将, 炎族大长老, 雷族大长老\n- 魂殿三天尊, 魂族祭坛主\n- 天魔蟒王, 菩提树灵, 古域兽王\n- 洞府守护龙魂, 帝品雏丹守护者\n- 联盟总指挥, 五帝破空之门守卫, 魂族大军统帅\n\nActually wait - let me look at this more carefully. The generic skill function `mob_skills_by_type()` is being called for all enemies not in ENEMY_NOVEL_SKILLS. The problem is that many named bosses aren't in that dict.\n\nLet me now go through each boss systematically and search the novel for their abilities. This is going to be a comprehensive task.\n\nLet me write a script that for each boss not yet covered, searches the novel for their name + combat context, and suggests skills based on what's found.","signature":"0c465330-7e30-4040-be73-1923b49c2a48"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3614,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":339200,"output_tokens":10060,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"stop_details":null},"type":"assistant","uuid":"e27808d2-9e5f-44e5-b680-072f164c53c6","timestamp":"2026-06-09T03:21:26.062Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"D:\\work\\wordworld","sessionId":"00d28fbf-7def-43f1-8f03-9196876513ea","version":"2.1.169","gitBranch":"master","slug":"eager-weaving-neumann"}
